headline: SimuTech Group Named 2025 Worldwide Channel Partner of the Year at Synopsys' Simulation and Analysis Global Sales Conference
summary: SimuTech Group, a leading provider of Ansys simulation software — now part of the Synopsys portfolio — alongside comprehensive consulting and training services, today announced it has been named 2025 Worldwide Channel Partner of the Year at Synopsys' Simulation and Analysis (S&A) Global Sales Conference.
